dr.inference.distribution
Class MixedDistributionLikelihood

java.lang.Object
  dr.inference.model.Likelihood.Abstract
      dr.inference.distribution.MixedDistributionLikelihood
All Implemented Interfaces:
Loggable, Likelihood, ModelListener, Identifiable, java.io.Serializable
public class MixedDistributionLikelihood
extends Likelihood.Abstract

A class that returns the log likelihood of a multidimensional statistic being distributed according to a mixture of parametric distributions, where the distribution membership of each element is determined by a separate vector of indices.
